{
  "name": "GS1 — Supabase Proxy v1.0",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## GS1 — Supabase Proxy v1.0\n\n**Purpose:** Authenticated proxy to Supabase that hides the anon key from the public dashboard source code.\n\n**Auth:** Validates GRID proxy token before any query runs. Returns 401 on failure.\n\n**Query types:**\n- `executions` — last N rows from executions table\n- `kpis` — today's counts + 24h success rate\n- `heatmap` — 7-day per-agent-per-day counts\n- `cost` — token usage sums (today + 7d)\n- `snapshots` — V3 workflow_snapshots\n\n**Deployed:** 2026-03-02\n**Webhook path:** /webhook/grid-supa-proxy",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 380
      },
      "id": "gs1-sticky",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [80, 60]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "GET",
        "path": "grid-supa-proxy",
        "options": {
          "responseHeaders": {
            "entries": [
              { "name": "Access-Control-Allow-Origin", "value": "*" }
            ]
          }
        },
        "responseMode": "responseNode"
      },
      "id": "gs1-webhook",
      "name": "Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [260, 340]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const PROXY_TOKEN = 'gfndr_px_yH7QMB5FwOu9Uu_jT41Y2mcE';\nconst incoming = $json.query?.token || '';\nif (!incoming || incoming !== PROXY_TOKEN) {\n  return [{ json: { __auth_failed: true } }];\n}\nconst type = $json.query?.type || 'executions';\nconst limit = Math.min(parseInt($json.query?.limit) || 20, 200);\nreturn [{ json: { ...$json, validated: true, queryType: type, queryLimit: limit } }];"
      },
      "id": "gs1-validate",
      "name": "Validate Token",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [480, 340]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": { "caseSensitive": true, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "strict" },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "auth-check",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.__auth_failed }}",
              "rightValue": true,
              "operator": { "type": "boolean", "operation": "equals" }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        }
      },
      "id": "gs1-auth-gate",
      "name": "Auth Failed?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [700, 340]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "json",
        "responseBody": "={ \"error\": \"Unauthorized\", \"code\": 401 }",
        "options": { "responseCode": 401 }
      },
      "id": "gs1-401",
      "name": "Respond 401",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [920, 220]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rules": {
          "values": [
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": {},
                "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.queryType }}", "rightValue": "kpis", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true, "outputKey": "kpis"
            },
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": {},
                "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.queryType }}", "rightValue": "heatmap", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true, "outputKey": "heatmap"
            },
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": {},
                "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.queryType }}", "rightValue": "cost", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true, "outputKey": "cost"
            },
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": {},
                "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.queryType }}", "rightValue": "snapshots", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true, "outputKey": "snapshots"
            }
          ]
        },
        "fallbackOutput": "extra"
      },
